cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for detecting groups of similar objects in medical images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of a hierarchical model and scope-based normalization features also suggests that the paper could be relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
